## Context
Resolved CodeRabbit critical thread on `src/monitors/worker.mjs` (PR #1). The `eventTail` monitor was appending its own `event_log_advanced` record into `events.ndjson` and then storing the pre-append size, so every tick observed the prior tick's write as a new "external" change and emitted again. Fix re-stats the file after the append so `lastEventSize` reflects the post-write size; on stat error falls back to the pre-append size. `npm test` (which exercises the event-tail spawn flow) passes.

